cs2410.assn3.directory

Class Person

  • java.lang.Object
    • cs2410.assn3.directory.Person

  • public class Person
extends java.lang.Object
    The Person class contains all relevant information on a given person needed for a student directory. Stores information such as name, ID, major, and age. Public functions allow each data member to be retrieved or changed. Constructor allows for the immediate initialization of each data member, as appropriate parameters are passed in.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Steven Proctor
